Surf_greatriver_sgx_v4_1

Hey there, finally it´s out :D The update of surf_greatriver_sgx_v4!!! I pushed the performance up so now the map is realy playable ^^ I fixxed the nade bug and the server will not crash anymore. 
The performance is now the same as xdre4m´s. I also fixxed some other things and made something new. 
It´s not a new version, just a update but this update rocks! So if you wanna have a new feeling of greatriver download and rate the map ;) 

Watch also my new mapping studio, R-Active Mapping
